# Alogyan — Automation Workflows

> **Stack**: Inngest (durable background jobs) + Firebase Firestore + WhatsApp Cloud API (or Twilio for SMS) + FCM (push notifications)
> **Time zone**: All cron schedules in `Asia/Kolkata` (IST).
> **Idempotency**: Every external call (WhatsApp, SMS, FCM) is wrapped with an idempotency key = `teacherId + workflowId + targetId + month/date` to prevent double-sends on retries.

---

## Workflow 1 — Monthly Fee Reminder

### Overview

Automatically remind students/parents about unpaid or partially paid fees at the start of every month.

### Trigger

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| Type | **Cron (scheduled)** |
| Schedule | `0 9 10 * *` — 10th of every month at 09:00 IST |
| Fallback | Also fires as event `fee/reminder.requested` when teacher manually clicks "Send Reminder" |

```
Every month on the 10th:
  → Scheduler fires cron trigger
  → Enqueues one workflow job per teacher (fan-out)
```

### Workflow Steps

```
[START]: monthly-fee-reminder
│
├─ Step 1: fetch-pending-fees
│    Query Firestore: fees WHERE
│      teacherId == ctx.teacherId
│      AND month == currentMonth
│      AND status IN ["pending", "partial", "overdue"]
│
├─ Step 2: group-by-student
│    Group fee records by studentId
│    Compute: totalDue, batchNames[], dueDate
│
├─ Step 3: send-messages (parallel fan-out)
│    For each student:
│    ├─ Step 3a: send-whatsapp → parentPhone
│    ├─ Step 3b: send-push-notification → student FCM token (if app installed)
│    └─ Step 3c: log-delivery-attempt → Firestore
│
└─ Step 4: update-reminder-log
     Write to Firestore: automationLogs/{id}
       { type: "fee_reminder", month, sentCount, failedCount, triggeredAt }
```

### Retry Policy

```
maxAttempts: 3
backoff: exponential (1 min → 5 min → 15 min)
onFailure: log to automationLogs with error details
```

### Message Template

**WhatsApp (parent phone):**
```
🔔 Fee Payment Reminder

Dear Parent of {{studentName}},

This is a gentle reminder that the tuition fee for 
*{{month}}* is pending.

📚 Batch: {{batchNames}}
💰 Amount Due: ₹{{totalDue}}
📅 Due Date: {{dueDate}}

Please make the payment at your earliest convenience.

For queries, contact: {{teacherPhone}}

— {{teacherName}} Sir/Ma'am
```

**FCM Push (student app):**
```
Title: 💰 Fee Reminder — {{month}}
Body:  ₹{{totalDue}} is due for {{batchNames}}. Please pay by {{dueDate}}.
Data:  { screen: "fees", month: "{{month}}" }
```

### Schedule Summary

```
Cron:    0 9 10 * *       Primary reminder (10th)
Cron:    0 9 20 * *       Second reminder (20th, only overdue ones)
Manual:  Event-triggered  Teacher clicks "Send Reminder" button
```

