## Workflow 3 — Test / Exam Reminder

### Overview

Remind students about upcoming tests 2 days before and again the morning of the test. Teacher creates a test event from the dashboard; the workflow is scheduled automatically.

### Trigger

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| Type | **Event-driven + delayed steps** |
| Event | `test/created` (fired when teacher saves a test) |
| Payload | `{ testId, batchId, subject, date, time, topics[], teacherId }` |

```
Teacher creates test → Event: test/created
  → Workflow starts
  → Step 1: sleep until (testDate - 2 days) at 18:00 IST
  → Step 2: send 2-day-before reminder
  → Step 3: sleep until (testDate) at 07:30 IST
  → Step 4: send morning-of reminder
```

### Workflow Steps

```
[EVENT]: test/created
│
├─ Step 1: validate-and-store
│    Read batch → get enrolled studentIds, parentPhones, FCM tokens
│    Store workflow state: testId, batchId, date, topics
│
├─ Step 2: sleep → until testDate - 2 days @ 18:00 IST
│    (Inngest native sleep, durable — survives restarts)
│
├─ Step 3: send-2day-reminder (parallel fan-out)
│    For each student:
│    ├─ send WhatsApp → parentPhone
│    └─ send FCM push → student device
│
├─ Step 4: sleep → until testDate @ 07:30 IST
│
├─ Step 5: send-morning-reminder (parallel fan-out)
│    Same as Step 3 but with "today is your test!" tone
│
├─ Step 6: send-post-test-check (optional)
│    sleep → until testDate + 3 days
│    Teacher prompted to enter results if no result submitted
│
└─ Step 7: log-completion
     Write automationLog: type "test_reminder", testId, sentCount
```

### Interrupt / Cancel

```
[EVENT]: test/cancelled or test/rescheduled
  → Cancel sleeping workflow using Inngest cancellation API
  → If rescheduled: re-queue new workflow with updated date
```

### Message Templates

**2-Day Before (WhatsApp — parent):**
```
📝 Test Reminder — {{subject}}

Dear Parent of {{studentName}},

A test is scheduled in *2 days*.

📚 Batch: {{batchName}}
📅 Date: {{testDate}} ({{dayOfWeek}})
⏰ Time: {{testTime}}
📖 Topics: {{topics}}

Please ensure your child is prepared.

— {{teacherName}} Sir/Ma'am
```

**Morning Of (FCM Push — student):**
```
Title: 📝 Test Today — {{subject}}
Body:  Your {{subject}} test is at {{testTime}}. Topics: {{topicsSummary}}. All the best! 🎯
Data:  { screen: "tests", testId: "{{testId}}" }
```

### Schedule Summary

```
Event: test/created       → Workflow starts immediately, sleeps internally
Event: test/cancelled     → Workflow cancelled
Event: test/rescheduled   → Old workflow cancelled, new one queued
Reminder 1: testDate - 2d @ 18:00 IST  (WhatsApp + FCM)
Reminder 2: testDate @ 07:30 IST       (WhatsApp + FCM)
```

