## Cross-Cutting Concerns

### Delivery Channel Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│               Notification Dispatcher Service            │
│                                                          │
│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌────────────────┐  │
│  │  WhatsApp   │  │  FCM Push   │  │  SMS (Twilio)  │  │
│  │ (wa.me link │  │  (Firebase) │  │  (fallback)    │  │
│  │  or Cloud   │  │             │  │                │  │
│  │    API)     │  │             │  │                │  │
│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └────────────────┘  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Opt-Out / DND Respect

Every student/parent record has an `optOut{}` field in Firestore:
```json
{
  "optOut": {
    "whatsapp": false,
    "sms": false,
    "push": false,
    "feeReminders": false
  }
}
```
All workflows check `optOut` before sending. Workflow skips silently with a log entry.

### Rate Limiting / Anti-Spam

| Rule | Limit |
|---|---|
| WhatsApp messages per parent per day | Max 5 |
| FCM push per student per day | Max 8 |
| Any single workflow run duration | 30 minutes |
| WhatsApp Cloud API sends per teacher per day | 1,000 (Business API limit) |

### Automation Log Schema (Firestore)

```
automationLogs/{logId}
  teacherId: string
  type: "fee_reminder" | "attendance_alert" | "test_reminder"
        | "announcement" | "payment_confirmation"
  status: "success" | "partial" | "failed"
  sentCount: number
  failedCount: number
  triggeredAt: Timestamp
  completedAt: Timestamp
  metadata: { month?, batchId?, testId?, announcementId?, feeRecordId? }
```

### Inngest Event Registry

| Event Name | Fired By | Consumed By |
|---|---|---|
| `attendance/marked` | Attendance API | Workflow 2 |
| `test/created` | Tests API | Workflow 3 |
| `test/cancelled` | Tests API | Workflow 3 (cancel) |
| `test/rescheduled` | Tests API | Workflow 3 (reschedule) |
| `announcement/published` | Announcements API | Workflow 4 |
| `fee/payment.recorded` | Fees API | Workflow 5 |
| `fee/reminder.requested` | Manual trigger (UI) | Workflow 1 |

---

## Summary Table

| # | Workflow | Trigger Type | Primary Channel | Schedule |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Fee Reminder | Cron + Manual | WhatsApp + FCM | 10th & 20th of month @ 09:00 IST |
| 2 | Attendance Alert | Event (real-time) | WhatsApp | Immediate on attendance mark |
| 3 | Test Reminder | Event + Sleep | WhatsApp + FCM | -2 days @ 18:00, test day @ 07:30 IST |
| 4 | Announcement Broadcast | Event (immediate/scheduled) | FCM + WhatsApp links | On publish or scheduled time |
| 5 | Payment Confirmation | Event (real-time) | WhatsApp + FCM | Immediate on payment record |
